full_text: All national media talking about Wolves celebrations being overboard only tells me that they don't have anything else to cry on or debate about 🤷🏽
Do you remember when you joined Twitter? I do! #MyTwitterAnniversary wow did not realize it was 3 years ago https://t.co/nwfDf87WQZ
The craziness of this off season has no end.  We could not have even 2 calm days. So far every no news day has become calm before the storm.
